Although Petro Symonenko, the Ukrainian Communist Party chief could be spreading a hoax, this story is sobering in its plausibility.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.themoscowtimes.com/stories/2002/09/23/009.html">Saddam could possibly have 200 nukes.</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
